latestPosts.caption:
Thoda baarish ka Maza liya jaye 

#baarish #mumbaibaarish #baarishein #monsoondiaries☔

Chokhi Dhani ek aisi jagah hai, mei toh bolunga Jaipur jao aur yaha ek shaam bitao. Yaha ka food, yaha ka culture ekdum topnotch, jo culture experience karne hum Jaipur gaye the voh saari cheezein hum yaha experience kar paye. Aur bhi bohot saari cheezein thi jo mujhe dikhani thi but ek reel kum pad jayegi, but jitna ho sake utna meine apna experience ek reel mein express kiya hai.

Aur bohot saari aisi experiences hai jo mei aap sabhi ke saath share karna chahta hu toh Follow karna buliyega matt!!💙

#chokhidhani #jaipurdiaries #chokhidhanijaipur #thingstodoinjaipur

latestPosts.caption:
Jaipur me mena kaafi unique cheeza dekhi aur experience kari, inn mese ek unique experience hai Hathi Gaon ka🐘🌳
Mena hathion ko zoo aur TV k alava kabhi ittne pass se nahi dekha hai aur unke sath ittni saari activities karne ka toh kabhi khayal bhi nahi aaya mujhe. Mena baachpan me ghodon ki savari khup ki hai parr hathi k peeth pe baith k Elephant Safari karne ka ye mera pahala experience tha. 

Aur bohot sari esi cheeza hai jo me aap sabhi k sath share karna chahata hu toh follow karna buliyega matt!💙🫶🏻

#elephant🐘 #jaipurdiaries #rajasthandiaries #safaripark
